      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DISTINCTION (2) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 4 lengths at Shepparton in a handy 24.65 beating Intrepidus. Winner at her latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Great chance again. CALY JET (7) is yet to miss the placings here in an excellent record which boasts two wins and two placings. Below best last time at The Meadows (30.72) in a Free For All, finishing a 12 length seventh. Looks a key chance on best figures. ONCE MORE (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.71 beating Crackerjack Trev. The form out of last race has been strong. Sure to be thereabouts. DEAR CARLA LOU (8) missed the frame latest (30.54) when sixth over 525m at The Meadows in a Free For All. Has six wins already from this draw.",
